1. To create/insert employee data
Request Method :POST
URL: http://localhost:8081/api/create
RequestBody : (JSON)
{
    "firstName":"nivetha",
    "lastName":"mohan",
    "emailId":"nivetha@gmail.com",
    "age":"27",
    "gender":"female",
    "address":"23sva anada bangalore"
}
2. To update existing employee data
Request Method: POST
URL:http://localhost:8081/api/update
RequestBody : (JSON)
{
    "id":1,
    "firstName":"prachi",
    "lastName":"priya prasad",
    "emailId":"prachi@gmail.com",
    "age":"22",
    "gender":"female",
    "address":"23sva anada  nilayabangalore"
}
3. To find all records that are not deleted
Request Method : GET
URL: http://localhost:8081/api/findAll
4. To find only deleted records 
Request Method: GET
URL: http://localhost:8081/api/findAllDeletedRecords
5. To find particular record based on id
Request Method: POST
URL:http://localhost:8081/api/findById
Request Body :(JSON)
{
"id":1
}
6.To delete a particular record by Id
Request Method: POST
URL : http://localhost:8081/api/deleteById
Request Body :(JSON)
{
"id":1
}


